name: Donny X
description: I am big fan of Faithless music and here you can read lyrics of their song Donny X. This beautiful melancholy is always in my heart. I used bamboo pen, transparent inks and droplets of water (mixed with my tears). This artwork made by Yana Almazova (@falsemercury) https://www.instagram.com/p/BwcITWHDleN/?igshid=4ieuhqukr0v9
